lead_paragraph: Shelby Rogers produced one of the biggest shocks at this year's French Open when she knocked out twice Wimbledon champion and 10th seed Petra Kvitova in the third round on Friday.

headline.print_headline: American Rogers, World Number 108, Sends Kvitova Packing
